{
  "local_port": 38396,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some good and romantic Malayalam songs?",
  "response": "Malayalam cinema is known for its soulful and melodious romantic songs that have touched the hearts of listeners for decades. Whether you're looking for timeless classics or contemporary hits, here's a curated list of some of the best and most romantic Malayalam songs:\n\n### **Classic Romantic Hits**\n\n1. **\"Mounamkal\"**  \n   - **Singer:** K.J. Yesudas  \n   - **Movie:** *Adimakal* (1983)  \n   A melodious track that beautifully captures the essence of love and longing.\n\n2. **\"Pavizha Mazha\"**  \n   - **Singer:** K.J. Yesudas  \n   - **Movie:** *Athiran* (2019)  \n   A serene and uplifting song that celebrates love amidst challenges.\n\n3. **\"Entammede Jimikki Kammal\"**  \n   - **Singers:** Vineeth Sreenivasan, Ranjith Unni  \n   - **Movie:** *Velipadinte Pusthakam* (2017)  \n   Though more upbeat, it's a romantic favorite at weddings and celebrations.\n\n### **Modern Romantic Favorites**\n\n4. **\"Entammede Jimikki Kammal\"**  \n   - **Singer:** Vineeth Sreenivasan  \n   - **Movie:** *Velipadinte Pusthakam* (2017)  \n   A lively yet romantic number that's widely loved.\n\n5. **\"Jimikki Kammal\"**  \n   - **Singer:** Vineeth Sreenivasan  \n   - **Movie:** *Velipadinte Pusthakam* (2017)  \n   An infectious tune that blends romance with vibrant energy.\n\n6. **\"Aaradhike\"**  \n   - **Singer:** Vijay Yesudas  \n   - **Movie:** *Pathemari* (2015)  \n   A heartfelt song expressing deep love and admiration.\n\n### **Soulful Ballads**\n\n7. **\"Aazhi Mazhayile\"**  \n   - **Singer:** K.S. Chithra  \n   - **Movie:** *Changathipoocha* (2017)  \n   A soothing ballad that delves into the nuances of love.\n\n8. **\"Kannarayiraal\"**  \n   - **Singers:** K.S. Chithra, Hariharan  \n   - **Movie:** *Pranayavarnangal* (1988)  \n   A timeless duet that remains a favorite among romantic songs.\n\n### **Contemporary Love Anthems**\n\n9. **\"Bimba\"**  \n   - **Singer:** Sooraj Santhosh  \n   - **Movie:** *Bimba* (2022)  \n   A modern track with poetic lyrics and a captivating melody.\n\n10. **\"Raagasiya Somayajyam\"**  \n    - **Singer:** Pradeep Palluruthy  \n    - **Movie:** *Raagasiya Somayajyam* (2021)  \n    A sweet and contemporary love song that's gained popularity recently.\n\n### **Popular Soundtracks**\n\n11. **\"Jimikki Kammal\"**  \n    - **Singer:** Vineeth Sreenivasan  \n    - **Movie:** *Velipadinte Pusthakam* (2017)  \n    A chartbuster that combines romance with catchy beats.\n\n12. **\"Pathiravayayi\"**  \n    - **Singers:** K.S. Chithra, Abhay Jodh  \n    - **Movie:** *C/O Saira Banu* (2017)  \n    A beautifully composed song that captures the magic of love.\n\n### **Emerging Hits**\n\n13. **\"Manjil Thullhu\"**  \n    - **Singer:** Madhu Balakrishnan  \n    - **Movie:** *Helen* (2019)  \n    A hauntingly beautiful song that portrays deep emotional ties.\n\n14. **\"Thaniye Mizhikal\"**  \n    - **Singer:** Vineeth Sreenivasan  \n    - **Movie:** *Thinking Out Loud* (2020)  \n    A melodious track blending modern sounds with romantic lyrics.\n\n### **Award-Winning Gems**\n\n15. **\"Neeyariyaan\"**  \n    - **Singer:** Shreya Ghoshal  \n    - **Movie:** *Jacobinte Swargarajyam* (2016)  \n    An award-winning song that beautifully expresses love and devotion.\n\n16. **\"Malare\"**  \n    - **Singer:** Vijay Yesudas  \n    - **Movie:** *Premam* (2015)  \n    A soulful melody that became an anthem for romantic enthusiasts.\n\n### **Instrumental Love Pieces**\n\n17. **\"Munthirival\"**  \n    - **Composer:** M. Jayachandran  \n    - **Movie:** *Loud Speaker* (2009)  \n    A lovely instrumental piece that evokes romantic feelings through its melody.\n\n### **Romantic Duets**\n\n18. **\"Kaatinu Chef Saji\"**  \n    - **Singers:** Vineeth Sreenivasan, Shreya Ghoshal  \n    - **Movie:** *Sapthamashree Thaskaraha* (2014)  \n    A delightful duet that beautifully narrates a romantic story.\n\n19. **\"Pranaya Kayala\"**  \n    - **Singers:** K.S. Chithra, Hariharan  \n    - **Movie:** *Mr. Pavanayi 99.99* (2019)  \n    A charming duet that explores the depths of love and connection.\n\n20. **\"Vennilave Vennilave\"**  \n    - **Singers:** Hariharan, K.S. Chithra  \n    - **Movie:** *Name* (2002)  \n    A mesmerizing song that captivates listeners with its romantic vibes.\n\n### **Recent Releases**\n\n21. **\"Jalajalochakkalla\"**  \n    - **Singer:** Vineeth Sreenivasan  \n    - **Movie:** *Kuruthi* (2021)  \n    A fresh romantic track that has gained popularity among the youth.\n\n22. **\"Karinkunnathe\"**  \n    - **Singer:** Pradeep Kumar  \n    - **Movie:** *Kappela* (2020)  \n    A soothing song that delves into modern love stories.\n\n### **Hidden Gems**\n\n23. **\"Kandam Becha Kottu\"**  \n    - **Singer:** Sithara Krishnakumar  \n    - **Movie:** *Action Hero Biju* (2016)  \n    A lesser-known track that's equally romantic and melodious.\n\n24. **\"Oru Madhuruginum\"**  \n    - **Singer:** Vijay Yesudas  \n    - **Movie:** *Njandukalude Nattil Oridavela* (2017)  \n    A sweet melody that beautifully portrays the innocence of love.\n\n### **Enduring Love Classics**\n\n25. **\"Ethu Sundara\"**  \n    - **Singers:** K.J. Yesudas, S. Janaki  \n    - **Movie:** *Chithram* (1988)  \n    A classic romantic duet that continues to resonate with audiences.\n\n---\n\nThese songs represent a mix of different eras and styles within the Malayalam music industry, each carrying its unique flavor of romance. Whether you're creating a romantic playlist, looking for the perfect song for a special occasion, or simply exploring Malayalam music, these tracks are sure to set the right mood.\n\nFeel free to explore these songs on your preferred music streaming platforms to experience their magic firsthand!",
